    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374670/extras/8d7c3251247f4f960db375982d809cde.poster.avif?t=1766078542\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374670/extras/8d7c3251247f4f960db375982d809cde.webm?t=1766078542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374670/extras/8d7c3251247f4f960db375982d809cde.mp4?t=1766078542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Duncrush是一款点击RPG游戏，你可以通过点击怪物进行攻击并征服充满挑战的地下城！<br>点击怪物以击败一波又一波的敌人，收集金币，获取强力的武器、盾牌和饰品。<br>通过丰富的技能树强化角色，并用独特的装备定制你的流派。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索多样化的地下城，每一个都有不同的挑战和奖励。<br>简单易上手的操作、令人上瘾的成长系统以及充满策略的地下城冒险，让Duncrush带给你点击与地牢探索双重乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374670/extras/6c2e09261efa4331278fdd6a0632f752.poster.avif?t=1766078542\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374670/extras/6c2e09261efa4331278fdd6a0632f752.webm?t=1766078542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374670/extras/6c2e09261efa4331278fdd6a0632f752.mp4?t=1766078542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单爽快的点击战斗体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集丰富的武器、盾牌和饰品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深度的技能树角色养成</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >策略性地下城攻略与激烈的Boss战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地下城的命运掌握在你的指尖！</p>",
